 '[{\"title\":\"What is payroll outsourcing, and how does it work?\",\"dec\":\"Payroll outsourcing is the method of hiring a third-party firm like Aone Outsourcing Solutions to manage payroll processing, employee payments, tax calculations, superannuation, and compliance. We handle everything, ensuring employees are paid accurately and on time while keeping your business ATO-compliant.\"},{\"title\":\"Why should I outsource my payroll services?\",\"dec\":\"Outsourcing payroll helps businesses:\\r\\n\\u2714 Save time and reduce administrative burden\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u2714 Ensure 100% compliance with Australian payroll laws and ATO regulations\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u2714 Avoid payroll errors and penalties\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u2714 Access expert payroll professionals without hiring an in-house team\\r\\n\\r\\n\\u2714 Reduce payroll processing costs\"},{\"title\":\"How much does outsourced payroll cost in Australia?\",\"dec\":\"The price of outsourcing payroll depends on three factors: business size the number of times payroll runs and the level of service complexity. Outsourcing payroll work provides lower costs than maintaining an internal payroll department and eliminates expenses related to payroll software as well as errors in compliance and costs associated with administrative duties.\"},{\"title\":\"Is payroll outsourcing safe and secure?\",\"dec\":\"Yes! Our payroll system at Aone Outsourcing Solutions protects your payroll data through encrypted cloud storage that maintains data security against all security threats.\"},{\"title\":\"What payroll software do you use?\",\"dec\":\"We work with leading payroll software, including Xero, MYOB, QuickBooks, Sage, NetSuite, ADP, and more, ensuring seamless integration with your existing business systems.\"},{\"title\":\"Does outsourced payroll include tax and superannuation compliance?\",\"dec\":\"Yes! We manage Single Touch Payroll (STP) lodgements, PAYG withholding, superannuation contributions, and payroll tax to keep your business compliant with ATO regulations.\"},{\"title\":\"What is Single Touch Payroll (STP), and why is it important?\",\"dec\":\"STP is an ATO-mandated payroll reporting system that requires businesses to deliver immediate real-time records on their employee salaries together with their tax deductions and superannuation payments to the government. Under our management, we process all reporting activities related to Single Touch Payroll (STP) to achieve complete compliance.\"}]', 'Y', 'Y', 'Get Professional and Expert Payroll Outsourcing Services that Can Elevate Your Payroll Process for Small Businesses in Australia!', 'Payroll Services in Australia'),
(32, 'SMSF Audit', NULL, '10886037801739252717.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">SMSF trustees must conduct an annual audit. When conducting an audit, it&#39;s important to remember that a licensed auditor must work with the Australian Securities Investments Commission. The main aim of the SMSF suit is to verify the accuracy and validity of the financial records.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Under Australian law, Self Managed Super Fund audits are mandatory, regardless of whether contributions were made or benefits received that year. The audit of SMSF aims to ascertain whether accounts, receipts, vouchers, and other evidence are accurately recorded and up-to-date; thus, it ascertains that the fund complies with the superannuation law.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">A trustee should conduct an annual high-quality SMSF audit on every fund to meet the SMSF requirements. The SMSF auditor must be appointed at least 45 days before the loss of a tax return submission to the ATO so that the auditor can prepare in advance.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://aone.makemybizprojects.co.in/public/uploads/process.png\" style=\"height:553px; width:620px\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Our Audit Services Tailored to Your SMSF Audit Needs</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Here are the SMSF Audit services provided by Aone Outsourcing Solutions:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong>Prepare Your SMSF Audit Files Effortlessly:</strong>&nbsp;Our outsourced SMSF audit online file preparation services include complete audit preparation, issue identification, and audit letters for your evaluation and approval.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li dir=\"ltr\">\r\n	<p dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><